name: SHSessionDelegate
desc: Methods that the session calls with the result of a match request.

items.name: func session(SHSession, didFind: SHMatch)
items.desc: Tells the delegate that the query signature matches an item in the catalog.

items.name: func session(SHSession, didNotFindMatchFor: SHSignature, error: Error?)
items.desc: Tells the delegate that the query signature doesn’t match an item in the catalog, or that there’s an error.
